                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <locus from="99v" to="103r"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="LIT7216HistoryJCRuf">History of how John Chrysostom visited the church of St Michael on an island</title>
                            <note>The text is acephalous. The text corresponds to <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet82#ms_i5"/>, where, however, the church is dedicated to the 
                                <ref type="pers" corresp="BPRS8083Raphael">Archangel Raphael</ref>.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown"/> ዘሀገረ፡ ቍስጥንጥንያ፡ ለአኖሬዎስ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ወይቤሎ፡ አእምር፡
